sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Human
    participant I as Interface CLI / UX
    participant K as HIA Kernel
    participant S as State Engine
    participant N as Session Engine
    participant C as Context Engine
    participant R as AI Router
    participant E as Executor
    participant O as Output Engine
    participant A as Artifacts / Radar

    H->>I: Request
    I->>K: Command / Intent
    K->>N: Check active session
    K->>S: Read current state
    S-->>K: State snapshot
    N-->>K: Session snapshot
    K->>C: Build context package
    C-->>K: Context package
    K->>R: Route task
    R->>E: Dispatch to executor/provider
    E-->>R: Result / patch / response
    R-->>K: Routing result
    K->>O: Validate output / edit
    O->>A: Update radar / artifacts / logs
    O->>S: Trigger state sync
    O->>N: Append session trace
    A-->>H: Evidence available